Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st0102.universalset Description

ST 0102 Universal Set-specific types.

ST0102 has two representations. The less common is as a Universal Set, and that is the usage supported by this package. The other representation is as a local set which is supported by org.jmisb.api.klv.st0102.localset.
